    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Habiti of new Priacma species, photographs of rock impressions. 1 — Priacma latidentata sp. nov., 2 — Priacma tuberculosa sp. nov., 3 — Priacma clavata sp. nov., 4 — Priacma renaria sp. nov." ;
